snippet: Top-seeded Caroline Wozniacki breezed into the semifinals of the E-boks Open in Copenhagen by defeating Alize Cornet of France, 6-0, 6-3.
abstract: Top-seeded Caroline Wozniacki defeats Alize Cornet to breeze into the semifinals of the E-boks Open tennis tournament in Copenhagen; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Caroline Wozniacki breezed into the semifinals of the E-boks Open in Copenhagen by defeating Alize Cornet of France, 6-0, 6-3.
